Exif.Name: Image Description
Exif.Description: Character string giving the title of the image. It may be a comment such as '1988 company picnic' for example. Two-bytes character codes cannot be used; instead, the Exif tag 'UserComment' is to be used

Exif.Name: Camera Make
Exif.Description: Manufacturer of the digital still camera (DSC), scanner, video digitizer or other equipment that generated the image. When this is left blank, it is treated as unknown

Exif.Name: Camera Model
Exif.Description: Model name or number of the digital still camera (DSC), scanner, video digitizer or other equipment that generated the image. When this is left blank, it is treated as unknown

Exif.Name: Horizontal Resolution
Exif.Description: Number of pixels per ResolutionUnit

Exif.Name: Vertical Resolution
Exif.Description: Number of pixels per ResolutionUnit

Exif.Name: Resolution Unit
Exif.Description: Unit for measuring Horizontal and Vertical resolutions

Exif.Name: Software
Exif.Description: Records the name and version of the software or firmware of the camera or image input device used to generate the image

Exif.Name: Date Time
Exif.Description: Date and time of image creation or when last modified

Exif.Name: Artist
Exif.Description: Records the name of the camera owner, photographer or image creator

Exif.StringValue: Copyright = Copyright Dan Petitt and CodeRanger.com. All rights reserved.
Exif.Name: Copyright
Exif.Description: Indicates both the photographer and editor copyrights; it is the copyright notice of the person or organization claiming rights to the image

Exif.Name: Exposure Time
Exif.Description: Exposure time in seconds

Exif.Name: F Number
Exif.Description: Camera F number

Exif.Name: Exposure Program
Exif.Description: Class of the program used by the camera to set exposure when the picture is taken

Exif.Name: ISO Speed Ratings
Exif.Description: Indicates the ISO Speed and ISO Latitude of the camera or input device as specified in ISO 12232

Exif.Name: Photo Exif Version
Exif.Description: Records version of this standard which is supported

Exif.Name: Date Time Original
Exif.Description: Date and time when the original image data was generated

Exif.Name: Photo Date Time Digitized
Exif.Description: Records date and time when the image was stored as digital data

Exif.Name: Shutter Speed
Exif.Description: Camera shutter speed used for this image

Exif.Name: Lens Aperture
Exif.Description: Camera lens aperture used for this image

Exif.Name: Brightness
Exif.Description: Camera brightness value

Exif.Name: Exposure Bias
Exif.Description: Camera exposure bias setting

Exif.Name: Metering Mode
Exif.Description: Metering mode

Exif.Name: Flash
Exif.Description: Indicates the status of flash when the image was shot

Exif.Name: Focal Length
Exif.Description: Actual focal length of the lens in mm

Exif.Name: Subject Location
Exif.Description: Indicates the location and area of the main subject in the overall scene

Exif.Name: Photo Maker Note
Exif.Description: Records additional desired information from the creator of the Exif data

Exif.Name: Photo Sub Sec Time Original
Exif.Description: Records fractions of seconds for DateTimeOriginal

Exif.Name: Photo Sub Sec Time Digitized
Exif.Description: Records fractions of seconds for DateTimeDigitized

Exif.Name: Photo Color Space
Exif.Description: Records the color space information

Exif.Name: Photo Pixel X Dimension
Exif.Description: Records the valid width of the meaningful image when it has been compressed

Exif.Name: Photo Pixel Y Dimension
Exif.Description: Records the valid height of the meaningful image when it has been compressed

Exif.Name: Photo Sensing Method
Exif.Description: Indicates the image sensor type on the camera or input device

Exif.Name: Photo Scene Type
Exif.Description: Indicates the type of scene. If a DSC recorded the image it will be set to 1, indicating that the image was directly photographed

Exif.Name: Photo Exposure Mode
Exif.Description: Indicates the exposure mode set when the image was shot

Exif.Name: Photo White Balance
Exif.Description: Indicates the white balance mode set when the image was shot

Exif.Name: Photo Focal Length In 35mm Film
Exif.Description: Indicates the equivalent focal length, assuming a 35mm film camera, in mm

Exif.Name: Photo Lens Specification
Exif.Description: Notes minimum focal length, maximum focal length, minimum F number in the minimum focal length and minimum F number in the maximum focal length, for the lens that was used

Exif.Name: Photo Lens Make
Exif.Description: Records the lens manufacturer

Gps.Description: Indicates horizontal positioning errors in meters
